properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Chincoteague to Parramore Island VA out 20 nm; Coastal waters from Fenwick Island DE to Chincoteague VA out 20 nm; Coastal waters from Parramore Island to Cape Charles Light VA out 20 nm
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 11 at 3:02AM EST until January 12 at 10:00AM EST by NWS Wakefield VA
properties.description:
* WHAT...South winds 20 to 30 kt with gusts 35 to 40 kt and waves
7 to 10 ft expected.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Fenwick Island DE to Chincoteague
VA out 20 nm, Coastal waters from Chincoteague to Parramore
Island VA out 20 nm and Coastal waters from Parramore Island
to Cape Charles Light VA out 20 nm.

* WHEN...From 7 PM this evening to 10 AM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 7 PM THIS EVENING TO 10 AM EST SUNDAY
